author: wn.com
title: UK Military Attache to Clarify Alleged Permission to Down Russian Planes
text: UK military attache is expected to clarify media reports of the alleged British leadership decision to enable Royal Air Force pilots participating in anti-ISIL coalition's airstrikes in Iraq to shoot down Russian aircraft, the Russian Defense Ministry press service said in a statement Sunday. ...
